description:
Mô Tả Công Việc


              Position Holder :	Distribution Compliance Senior Supervisor

              Department:	Distribution Compliance (DC) Legal, Compliance & Internal Control

              Reports to:	DC Manager


              Purpose of this role:

              -	Mainly take charge of dealing with misconducts of insurance distribution channels, including alternative agents and related staff.

              -	Support corporate compliance function in handling tasks where assigned by manager in financial crime and anti-fraud matters.


              Main Responsibility

              1.	Investigate violations of sales force, including alternative agents, staff and propose adequate punishments to the violating agents/ staffs in accordance with Company’s rules, regulations of IAV, and the applicable insurance laws;

              2.	Self make comprehensive and efficient plans on examining and investigating alternative agents/ staff misconducts happened;

              3.	Recognize potential violations by sales force/ staff and propose solutions to mitigate harm may occur;

              4.	Develop, review internal rules on sales force activities misconduct handling;

              5.	Conduct training sharing/audit/on-site, off-site inspection to sales force;

              6.	Undertake other responsibilities as assigned by the manager from time to time.


              Key Result Area

              - Conclude violations by relevant agents/ staff properly and come out adequate disciplinary proposals in accordance with the applicable laws, IAV’s and internal regulations;

              - Effectively organize agency compliance trainings;

              - Manage assigned tasks well and timely report to the manager.


              Xem toàn bộ Mô Tả Công Việc
